00:25:58,110 --> 00:26:00,060
Wait, what bed did you say she was on?

542
00:26:00,110 --> 00:26:01,080
Mine.

543
00:26:01,750 --> 00:26:03,160
I'm sure I put her on my bed.

544
00:26:03,210 --> 00:26:05,100
No, she was definitely on my bed.

545
00:26:05,150 --> 00:26:07,450
Why would I kiss a girl and then put her on your bed?

546
00:26:08,710 --> 00:26:10,280
Well, then who was on my bed?

547
00:26:10,330 --> 00:26:12,110
Oh, oh, oh...

548
00:26:14,220 --> 00:26:15,870
No! No! No!

549
00:26:16,180 --> 00:26:17,510
Yes!

550
00:26:18,750 --> 00:26:20,740
You were under the pile of coats?

551
00:26:20,790 --> 00:26:23,200
I was the pile of coats!

552
00:26:26,600 --> 00:26:28,070
Oh, my God!

553
00:26:29,400 --> 00:26:32,390
You were my midnight mystery kisser?!

554
00:26:33,780 --> 00:26:36,580
You were my first kiss with Rachel?!

555
00:26:37,870 --> 00:26:40,260
You were my first kiss ever?!

556
00:26:42,820 --> 00:26:45,050
What did I marry into?!

557
00:27:19,850 --> 00:27:21,430
Crap!

